{
  "texts": [
    "Further, inadequate follow-up has been a limitation with regards to identifying false negative diagnoses (21).",
    "Notably, users may not be adequately protected from the risks of using smartphone diagnostic apps by Conformit Europenne (CE) certification, which endorsed two apps with flaws (SkinVision and TeleSkin's skinScan app).",
    "A prospective trial of SkinVision found low sensitivity and specificity for melanoma classification (22).",
    "In contrast to CE, the US Food and Drug Administration's (FDA) requirements for endorsement are more stringent (21).",
    "Artificial intelligence applications can enhance skin cancer screening in the primary care setting and streamline referrals to dermatologists."
  ]
}